high_descs: Go to the table on your left, to the left of the coffee maker.
Pick up the tomato from the table
Turn right and go to the fridge.
Chill the tomato and take it out of the fridge.
Go back to the table to the left of the coffee maker.
Put the tomato on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled tomato on the table to the left of the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn to your left and walk to the front of the white table.
Pick up the tomato near the wall at the back of the table.
Turn to your right and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and place the tomato on the top rack, close the fridge door; after cooling, open the fridge door and pick up the tomato, close the fridge door.
Turn to your left and walk to the front of the white table at the end with the head of lettuce on it.
Put the tomato near the front edge of the table and to the right of the spoon.
anns.task_desc: Refrigerate a tomato, place it on the table

high_descs: Walk to the left to face the table.
Pick up the tomato from the table.
Walk to the right and face the refrigerator.
open the door and put the tomato inside. Wait few seconds open the door and pick it up again
Walk to the left and face the table.
Put the tomato back on the table beside the spoon.
anns.task_desc: Put the tomato to the refrigerator and return it to the table.
